name: Hey, how are you?
description:
Deadlines with my Demons #3
#Herbie7777777
CN
--------------
Whenever I would go to his house I would greet him with: "Na, wie gehts?"
We would never shake hands or anything. 
The apartment smelled moldy and was dimly lit.
After a while of talking about random stuff, the conversation would drift towards recent movies, video games or which game I'd like to play. I think.
I would then sit down on the couch. His TV was large and bright.

My memories start to get foggy here. 
What my age is? I don't know.
